<div class='allCommunityAnswers'>
<div class='communityAnswer'>
<div class='communityAnswerBody'>
<div class='answererUserIcon'>
<a class="leftAlignedImage userPhoto" href="/user/show/18688312-gerry"><img alt="" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/users/1488530482i/18688312._UY100_CR7,0,100,100_.jpg" /></a>
</div>
<div class='communityAnswerTextContainer'>
<span class='communityAnswererName'>
<a href="/user/show/18688312-gerry">Gerry</a>
</span>
<span class='communityAnswerText'>
The paperback has 350 pages, of which 277 are narrative; the back pages are appendices.
</span>
</div>
