<span id="freeTextContainer18159887393102514669">An 8 hour and 45 minute unabridged audiobook.<br/><br/>The author really knows how to craft a story and keep the readers attention. Just random tidbits of personal information such as what a particular general had for breakfast before reviewing battle reports. It reads as a novel while covering actual historical events. I really liked it.</span>

