              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/666003-silvana?shelf=illustrated-editions">illustrated-editions</a>
          </div>
    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer1979796340" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer5252997412713864072">In less than one month, we are going to celebrate the 75th year of D-day. Or, in Field Marshall Rommel&apos;s own words: The Longest Day. <br/><br/>I am lucky that my reread of this book is the 70th anniversary collector&apos;s edition. The additional materials, war diaries, photos and interviews are truly fascinating. Go get this version if you can. You could even get used to the small fonts as the materials are so engrossing. <br/><br/>My original review:<br/><a target='_blank' rel='noopener nofollow' href='https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/24688744'>https://www.goodreads.com/review/show...</a></span>
